.cm SCRIPT REFERENCE AR
.SUBT Purpose
The ARABIC control word causes page numbers to use arabic numerals.
.SUBT Format
×
×  .AR
×
.SUBT Usage
The .AR control word causes all page numbers produced hereafter in
headings or footings to be printed in
arabic numerals.
.SUBT Defaults
Page numbering in
arabic is in effect until an ".ro" is
encountered.  A break is not created by this command.
.SUBT Notes
.of 4
(1) Arabic numerals are the normal mode.
.sp 1
.of 4
(2) The ARABIC control word is equivalent to ".PN
.cm End of AR
